body:
As a student, I benefited a few class lessons about mobile adaptation. This simple Paint application is the result of these lessons.

You could try this app on:
* desktop: as Firefox does not have any Color input elements, a basic but adaptive solution has been impemented ;
* mobile: there are touch support, portrait/landscape adaptation, and also benefits the previous solution relative to the lack of support of Color input ;

